imilarly-sized\npopulation of rapid AM reorienters with large $\\Psi_\\mathrm{int}$, implying\nthat a large $\\Psi_\\mathrm{int}$ is not a sufficient condition for major axis\nrotation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2022 18:57:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
