when using the asteroseismic scaling\nrelations. This revision brings the asteroseismic properties into an agreement\nwith those determined from eclipsing binaries. The new correction factor and\nthe stellar models with the corrected frequencies are available at\n{https://www.github.com/parallelpro/surface}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2022 00:06:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 13 May 2023 12:02:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 16 May 2023 03:42:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-24"}
