ortices sheds light on this\nstage of transition. In both cases, cross-flow effects dominate the flow\ndynamics, suggestings the need to consider these effects when modelling\nsuperhydrophobic surfaces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2022 12:51:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-03"}
